sky.f1.uk.title: Peter Wright: Double Champ 20 & 22

sky.f1.uk.title: Gerwyn Price: Welsh Glory 2021

sky.f1.uk.title: The Greatest Leg - 2023 Final
sky.f1.uk.description: In 2023, both MVG and Michael Smith were on course to record a nine-dart leg; the Dutchman fell short by a single dart, but the Englishman achieved perfection. Ep 10.

sky.f1.uk.title: 30 Years of the PDC World Champs'
sky.f1.uk.description: In celebration of 30 years of the PDC World Darts Championship, take a look back at the very first tournament, a classic final from 2007 and one of the greatest legs ever played. Ep 1.

sky.f1.uk.title: The Taylor Years
sky.f1.uk.description: Hear from the legendary Phil Taylor as the 16-time world champion recounts his glory years at the PDC World Darts Championship. Ep 2.

sky.f1.uk.title: The Greatest Final 07:Taylor v RVB
sky.f1.uk.description: In the final act at the Circus Tavern, two of the finest players to have ever played the sport created a match for the ages, as Phil Taylor and Raymond van Barneveld met in the final. Ep 3.

sky.f1.uk.title: WDC 2026: The Story So Far

sky.f1.uk.title: WDC 2026: The Story So Far

sky.f1.uk.title: WDC 2026: The Story So Far

sky.f1.uk.title: WDC 2026: The Story So Far

sky.f1.uk.title: WDC 2026: The Story So Far

tnt1.title: Premier League Review: 2011/12
tnt1.description: A review of the 2011/12 season. As the competition entered its 20th year, Man City won their first title in dramatic fashion and Wigan produced a great escape to avoid the drop.

tnt1.title: Premier League Review: 2012/13
tnt1.description: A review of the 2012/13 season. Sir Alex Ferguson ended his managerial career as Manchester United clinched their 13th Premier League title and FA Cup winners Wigan were relegated.

tnt1.title: Premier League Review: 2013/14
tnt1.description: A review of the 2013/14 season. Manchester City clinched their second Premier League title, Jose Mourinho returned to Chelsea and Tony Pulis masterminded a great escape at Palace.

tnt1.title: Premier League Review: 2014/15
tnt1.description: A review of the 2014/15 season. Eden Hazard's superb form helped Chelsea clinch their fifth title, while newly-promoted Burnley and QPR made immediate returns to the Championship.

tnt1.title: Premier League Review: 2015/16
tnt1.description: A review of the 2015/16 season. Leicester City shocked the footballing world, Jose Mourinho's second tenure at Chelsea came to an end and Newcastle dropped into the second tier.

tnt1.title: Premier League Review: 2016/17
tnt1.description: Take a look back at the 2016/17 Premier League season as Chelsea win their fifth Premier League title and reigning champions Leicester set a new record for worst title defence.

tnt1.description: Action from Serie A as Genoa and Atalanta go head-to-head at Stadio Luigi Ferraris. Atalanta beat Genoa 4-0 in the Coppa Italia earlier this month.

tnt1.title: The Monuments
tnt1.description: Spanning Germany and Austria, the Four Hills tournament is the pinnacle of ski jumping.We dive into the drama, rivalries, and cultural aspects of this iconic event.

tnt1.description: A look back at the 2017/18 Premier League season as Manchester City win their third title, Mohamed Salah scores 32 goals for Liverpool and Stoke's top flight status ends.

tnt1.title: Premier League Review: 2018/19
tnt1.description: A look back at the 2018/19 Premier League season that was competitive until the very end, with fans captivated by an epic title race between Manchester City and Liverpool.

tnt1.title: Premier League Review: 2019/20
tnt1.description: A look back at the 2019/20 Premier League season as a pandemic-disrupted season saw Liverpool win their first ever Premier League title.

tnt1.description: A look back at the 2020/21 Premier League season as Manchester City regained the title and won their fifth Premier League title.

tnt1.title: Premier League Review: 2021/22
tnt1.description: A look back at all the highs and lows from an epic 2021/22 Premier League season, which saw a thrilling title race between Man City and Liverpool come down to the final day.

tnt1.description: A review the biggest stories and best action from 2022/23 Premier League season, as Pep Guardiola's Manchester City look to secure a third consecutive title.

tnt1.description: We revisit all the drama and best action from the 2023/24 Premier League season. Manchester City were looking to become the first side to win four EPL titles in a row.

E4Plus1.uk.description: The Wedding Gift Wormhole: A stressed Sheldon and Amy struggle to work out what the 'perfect gift' is that Leonard and Penny gave them on their wedding day. (S12 Ep2)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: A Springfield Summer Christmas for Christmas: A cable channel films a Christmas movie in Springfield, and Skinner falls in love. (S32 Ep10)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Manger Things: A secret from Flanders' past is revealed, and we discover a room in the Simpsons' home that we've never seen before. (S32 Ep16)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Rude(ish) Tube Shorts
E4Plus1.uk.description: A short, cheeky clip from Rude Tube's naughty little sister Rude(ish) Tube, featuring sheep.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Fleming: Gordon Ramsay visits Fleming, a Danish restaurant in Miami. It was once the best family-run restaurant in town but is now losing money fast. (S3 Ep6)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Sushi Ko: Akira and Lisa are losing up to $20,000 a month at their sushi restaurant in California. Can Gordon piece the family back together and save the restaurant? (S3 Ep7)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Thanksgiving Decoupling: Howard takes the gang to his mother's house for Thanksgiving to protect himself from his grumpy father-in-law who has also been invited. (S7 Ep9)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Discovery Dissipation: Sheldon feels guilty when he gets attention for his accidental discovery of a new element. Raj stays with Howard and Bernadette for a week. (S7 Ep10)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Cooper Extraction: Sheldon has to go back to Texas when his sister goes into labour. While he's away, the gang gather at the flat to decorate the Christmas tree. (S7 Ep11)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Hesitation Ramification: Penny's big TV acting break hits the cutting-room floor, so Leonard does his best to comfort her, which leads her to ask him a bold question. (S7 Ep12)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Playing with Fire
E4Plus1.uk.description: (2019) Fun-filled family comedy starring John Cena. A macho fireman has to babysit three impish kids after saving them from a blaze in the remote California woodlands.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Sonic the Hedgehog
E4Plus1.uk.description: (2020) Madcap adventure-comedy video game adaptation with Jim Carrey and Ben Schwartz. Can nippy ring-chasing hedgehog Sonic escape the clutches of an evil, moustachioed scientist?

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Sales Call Sublimation: Penny gets more than she bargained for when Leonard meets a psychiatrist, while Sheldon and Raj make an astronomical discovery. (S9 Ep12)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Empathy Optimization: The gang plan a Sheldon-free weekend in Las Vegas after coping with his constant demands, rudeness and ingratitude when he was ill. (S9 Ep13)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Meemaw Materialization: Sheldon is thrilled when his beloved grandma 'Meemaw' comes to visit, but his excitement fades when she butts heads with Amy. (S9 Ep14)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Valentino Submergence: Sheldon and Amy host a special live Valentine's Day episode of their internet show Fun with Flags. Leonard and Penny grapple with getting older. (S9 Ep15)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Positive Negative Reaction: When Bernadette makes a big announcement, Howard becomes convinced that he needs to start earning more money. (S9 Ep16)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Celebration Experimentation: The gang persuade Sheldon to celebrate his birthday and invite a few special guests along to his party, in the 200th episode. (S9 Ep17)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Application Deterioration: Leonard, Sheldon and Howard run into problems when they file for a patent. Emily reaches out to Raj after their break-up. (S9 Ep18)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Independence Day
E4Plus1.uk.description: (1996) Blockbusting landmark sci-fi action-thriller starring Will Smith and Jeff Goldblum. A US Air Force pilot and a scientist battle aliens who are spectacularly destroying our planet.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Celebrity Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: The celebrities watch: This Morning, Dating Around, Mission: Impossible - Rogue Nation, Hostile Planet, Big Brother: Best Shows Ever, EastEnders and The Repair Shop. (S2 Ep4)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Celebrity Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: The celebrities watch 127 Hours, Planet Earth II, Cape Fear, This Morning on public toilets, EastEnders, Bradley Walsh & Son: Breaking Dad, and BBC News on beaches. (S2 Ep5)

Film4.uk.description: (2022) Lesley Manville stars as a cleaner who saves up and heads to Paris to get herself a Dior couture dress, in director Anthony Fabian's fabulous, Oscar-nominated period comedy drama.

Film4.uk.title: The Invitation
Film4.uk.description: (2022) Gothic horror with Nathalie Emmanuel. A struggling New York artist discovers she has rich British relatives and accepts an invitation to a wedding in Whitby. Well, blood is blood.

Film4.uk.title: Step Brothers
Film4.uk.description: (2008) Outrageous comedy with Will Ferrell and John C. Reilly. When two 40-year-old man-children's parents marry, can the lads settle their differences and grow up? Strong language/nudity.

Film4.uk.description: Teleshopping.

Film4.uk.title: The Muppets Take Manhattan

Film4.uk.title: Tooth Fairy
Film4.uk.description: (2010) Family fantasy comedy. Dwayne Johnson stars as a tough ice hockey player who is transformed into a real-life fairy as punishment for telling a child that tooth fairies don't exist.

Film4.uk.title: The Devil Wears Prada
Film4.uk.description: (2006) Comedy-drama starring Anne Hathaway and Meryl Streep. A naive young woman lands a job as assistant to one of New York's most important, but ruthless and cynical, magazine editors.

Film4.uk.title: The Equalizer
Film4.uk.description: (2014) Thriller. Denzel Washington stars as an ex-soldier who comes out of retirement to help a teenage sex worker who's been assaulted by her pimp.

Film4.uk.title: Three Billboards Outside...
Film4.uk.description: ...Ebbing, Missouri: (2017) Oscar-winning dark comedy about a mother who wants the cops to solve her daughter's murder using three precisely worded billboards. Starring Frances McDormand.

Film4.uk.title: Wish You Were Here
Film4.uk.description: (1987) Award-winning comedy-drama set in an English seaside town in the early 1950s. Emily Lloyd stars as a spirited teenager whose sexual awakening comes at a price. With Tom Bell.

Film4.uk.title: Mr Popper's Penguins
Film4.uk.description: (2011) Family comedy. Jim Carrey stars as a work-obsessed New York property developer whose life is turned upside down when he receives a crate containing six live penguins.

Film4.uk.title: Deck the Halls
Film4.uk.description: (2006) Comedy. Neighbours Matthew Broderick and Danny DeVito get extremely competitive as they festoon their houses with increasingly outrageous festive decorations and lights.

Film4.uk.title: Sleepless in Seattle
Film4.uk.description: (1993) Romantic comedy with Tom Hanks and Meg Ryan. A bereaved man gets another chance at love when his son puts him on a radio talk show.

Film4.uk.title: Moonfall

Film4.uk.title: Romancing the Stone
Film4.uk.description: (1984) Comedy action adventure starring Michael Douglas and Kathleen Turner. An adventurer helps a bestselling author to search for her sister, who's been kidnapped in Colombia.
